      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the profound sense of loss you are feeling, and while no one can fully replicate that specific devastation, your perspective is one of deep despair that no amount of advice can truly fix. Please know that even when you feel entirely broken, there are always others who can sit with you in that darkness without trying to \"fix\" it immediately. If you are willing, I can help you find resources specifically for individuals grieving major identity crises or existential collapse, as this is a unique and valid form of pain.",
